Fuck Arabs
[[Image:Jasmine_fucking.jpg|thumb|right|Fuck Arabs, man. Fuck 'em right in the ass.]]
{{ljcomm|fuck_arabs}} is a [[LiveJournal]] community that was taken over by an army of novice trolls.

==Origins==
Back in September of 2004, a pissed-off 17-year-old [[furry]] named {{lj|rayne_vandunem}} created a community called "[[Fuck]] [[Arabs]]." Being a gigantic pussy, however, he promptly [http://community.livejournal.com/africandiaspora/4486.html apologized] and tried to weasel out of what he'd done by claiming [[O_rly|he was only against the Arabs ''in power'', not all the Arabs.]]

Along came irate nationalist and [[Internet tough guy]] {{lj|americanbulldog}}, who had no problems whatsoever with looking like a racist. He decided that "Fuck Arabs" was a great name for a meeting-place for like-minded [[racist]]s and [[liberal]]-haters to get together and complain about the towelheads, and so he took over from {{lj|rayne_vandunem}}. His [http://community.livejournal.com/fuck_arabs/402.html first post] was a long string of neocon cliches and xenophobic rambling, all delivered in the pseudomilitaristic style white supremacists pick up from their relatives who washed out of the Marines.

Expecting a slew of new friends to appear, American Bulldog set his LJ mood as "accomplished" and sat back to await the praise and privileges that were his due.

==The takeover==
Within 24 hours, Arab LJ users {{lj|sabotabby}}, {{lj|habibi}}, and {{lj|kynn}} banded together and declared jihad on the new community, except with a lot less religious crap and a lot more lulz.

The next post?

'''[http://community.livejournal.com/fuck_arabs/1077.html I LOVE ARAB FUCKING]'''

{{squote|one time i had a boyfriend that knew the [[commie]] sutra backwards. apparently it applies to boy on boy sex because we fucked all night in crazy positions and a lot of massage too. i've never had better sex, certainly not with any american boy blockheads who's semen has more steroids than cow feed and lowers your IQ each time they shoot it into you.

FUCK AMERICAN WHITE BOYS, ARAB LOVE FOREVER!!!|loveislife, [http://community.livejournal.com/fuck_arabs/1077.html here]}}

Poor American Bulldog and the few trailer park refugees who'd been cheated out of their 7/11 jobs by those dirty sand niggers were shocked to find that a bunch of gay homo liberals had infiltrated their community, flooding it with posts about [http://community.livejournal.com/fuck_arabs/2701.html Arab porn], [http://community.livejournal.com/fuck_arabs/7384.html more Arab porn], [http://community.livejournal.com/fuck_arabs/3196.html sandy vaginas], and [http://community.livejournal.com/fuck_arabs/9035.html still more Arab porn]. Community members expressed their desire to fuck such diverse candidates as Ralph Nader, Frank Zappa, Tony Shalhoub, and [http://community.livejournal.com/fuck_arabs/10488.html Osama bin Laden] (you know he's a naughty boy). Even [[Rule 34]] [http://community.livejournal.com/fuck_arabs/25903.html#cutid1 made an appearance].

==The aftermath==
After 135 posts in 24 hours, American Bulldog [http://community.livejournal.com/fuck_arabs/44115.html turned over the reins of the community] to {{lj|mp_reyart}} and promptly [[Deleting your LiveJournal|committed e-seppuku]], except not seppuku because that's for gay Japs. The community, now with a kitschy [[pirate]] theme, went dead within a week as the novelty wore off, but there are still 245 members and the occasional post about hot Arab chicks, which is probably more activity than the jingoists would've managed.

